@host = http://localhost:3002
@baseUrl = {{host}}/api

### -----------------------------------------------------------------
### API Root
### -----------------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}

### -----------------------------------------------------------------
### Blockchain
### -----------------------------------------------------------------

### Return the full blockchain
GET {{baseUrl}}/chain

### Return whether the chain is valid
GET {{baseUrl}}/chain/valid

### -----------------------------------------------------------------
### Transactions
### -----------------------------------------------------------------
### Add a pending transaction
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAddress": "3056301006072a8648ce3d020106052b8104000a03420004b601085afa97744664bb78ae952bcf982aaf97315c7cbc9fb5e86836816972f31d0cd1003cc324808a5b518b7d27c53e6b256525f07ce20540e5473e9395efd0",
  "toAddress": "3056301006072a8648ce3d020106052b8104000a034200042794a32c99af2d8cd3890f108d3b5dbabf73f6e23ae99ea68613e0716c0bd3733f4a6f4e35e842a61d08ca33f548b189628fb9f1f4bc50c7a86aea6218968016",
  "amount": 25,
  "signature": "3046022100b8fdced49cb3998e0f67fa000e7e34ca2fa2f56dfc018615cc431b2fe3c4a98e0221009147b6ed9afef69acc95eae1ccc2d96aa15b159f20ae27d36775cbb97648e1d1"
}

### View pending transactions
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions/pending

### View confirmed transactions
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions

### -----------------------------------------------------------------
### Mining
### -----------------------------------------------------------------
### Mine the pending transactions
POST {{baseUrl}}/mine
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "minerAddress": "miner-1"
}

### -----------------------------------------------------------------
### Balance
### -----------------------------------------------------------------
### Get an address balance
@USER1=address1
GET {{baseUrl}}/balance/{{USER1}}

### -----------------------------------------------------------------
### Statistics
### -----------------------------------------------------------------
### View chain and mining statistics
GET {{baseUrl}}/stats

### -----------------------------------------------------------------
### Wallets
### -----------------------------------------------------------------
### Generate a wallet-like key pair
POST {{baseUrl}}/wallets

### View a balance for a wallet address
@USER2=address2
GET {{baseUrl}}/wallets/{{USER2}}